and then live ammunition 
the rioting in which 140 arabs were wounded was the bloodiest 
of the palestinian uprising against israeli occupation that began 
in december 1987 
in the uprising at least 758 palestinians have been slain by 
israelis and another 278 arabs have been killed by other arabs as 
alleged collaborators with the enemy fiftytwo israelis and 
foreigners have also died in the violence 
moslems venerate the temple mount as haram essharif or the 
