<TEXT>
the maharishi mahesh yogi said thursday 
his solution to the persian gulf crisis was to have hundreds of 
thousands of professional meditators mediate worldwide to try to 
harmonize world consciousness 
the maharishi leader of the transcendental meditation movement 
told an internationally broadcast news conference in the 
netherlands that the united nations is like a dead body and 
only mass meditation can bring bliss 
he said 7000 skilled meditators in the gulf region could 
improve regional and international atmospheres and make peace 
inevitable 
we cannot rely anymore on the political arena of the world 
the maharishi said from his european headquarters in the dutch city 
of vlodrop 
governments and political organizations are incompetent to 
bring about peace and are of no significance 
what happened to kuwait now can happen to any country or 
little emirate here and there all the military might and efforts 
against terrorism are not succeeding 
his meditation peace plan for the gulf was heard at the united 
nations and in washington austin texas cleveland boston kansas 
city chicago ottawa montreal and toronto 
two days ago the united nations was the site of an international 
tv hookup to commemorate what would have been the 50th birthday of 
the late john lennon one of the beatles who were followers of the 
maharishi 
un officials said they make un conference rooms available to 
worthy organizations without any rental fee and bill them only for 
the cost of services and overtime 
at the yogic hookup thursday only about 30 professional people 
in business suits and a few journalists gathered in a small 
basement conference room at un headquarters and there was no 
transcendental meditation 
after an opening statement the maharishi took questions asked 
about the united nations that recently has had some peacekeeping 
success he said it is a nebulous organization the 
security council cannot guarantee security to any part of the 
world its like a dead body 
he said in answer to a question that un peacekeepers with 
light sidearms should be replaced by professional paid meditators 
that would be more successful and productive he said 
un efforts in the gulf have failed the maharishi said 
that is why we appeal to the people of the world to be united 
now 
his followers claim that 7000 is a magic number for creating a 
powerful meditative consciousness that can affect urroundings and 
behavior they say this has been proved in more than 500 scientific 
studies 
the maharishi said responsible governments should designate 
special groups of 7000 people who then would be taught meditation 
and a form of levitation 
we would train them to fly and that would be the end of all 
unfortunate evils in the world 
the title maharishi signifies a hindu teacher of mysticism 
