economically pressed argentina wants 
to enter opec according to a news report thursday 
argentine president carlos menem was quoted by venezuelas 
government news agency venpres as saying argentina plans to free 
its domestically controlled energy prices in january and to 
increase foreign oil sales so it can join the organization of 
