increasing them to reach our goals menem was quoted as saying 
menem has been president of argentina which has rich natural 
resources but has been debilitated by years of chronic economic and 
labor problems since july 8 1989 
he said argentine oil now earns nearly 400 million per year 
argentina is a country with oil and it has the option of 
gradually increasing exports menem said 
venezuela and ecuador are the only latin american members of the 
