turning himself in to authorities sunday that led to the arrest of 
the eight spies whose crimes were outlined by the chief federal 
prosecutors office thursday 
late thursday the cologne newspaper express said kurons former 
east german control officer had also been arrested there was no 
immediate confirmation from authorities 
one of the group of eight arrested identified only as karlheinz 
s allegedly passed on directly to the soviet kgb information 
about a new tank under development the chief federal prosecutor 
said 
