germans information and documents about military helicopters 
the prosecutor said the agent obtained the information while 
working for messerschmidtboelkowbloehm the largest west german 
aerospace manufacturer 
two other people are accused of handing over to the east germans 
information about the development of natos sophisticated tornado 
fighter jet they allegedly took pictures of the original 
topsecret documents and passed them on to the soviet bloc agents 
all eight of those arrested come from west germany according to 
