names of those arrested but the spokesmen had already left for the 
day and were unreachable at home 
where the latest round of arrests and disclosures will stop no 
one knows von stahl says more developments are expected and he 
has a pool of 8000 former east german spies to pick from in the 
coming months 
leaders of the former east german security service known as the 
stasi are believed to have abetted some of international 
terrorists news reports say the terrorists may still be lurking on 
german soil 
